OL,3,CGuernsey students left frustrated over
OL,4,Clow GCSE pass rates for maths
OL,6,FStudents and tutors in Guernsey are
OL,7,Fblaming a lack of consistent teaching
OL,8,Ffor low GCSE Maths pass rates.
OL,10,FIt comes as figures from the States
OL,11,Freveal that just 52% of the island's
OL,12,Fstudents obtained a passing grade four
OL,13,For above in maths last year - 8% lower
OL,14,Fthan the UK.
OL,16,FUnions point to a lack of teacher
OL,17,Fretention as one of the primary
OL,18,Fissues, with pupils also citing
OL,19,Flimited support for maths.
