OL,3,CGuernsey students left frustrated over
OL,4,Clow GCSE pass rates for maths
OL,6,FMeena Du Plessis, 18, has not passed
OL,7,Fher GCSE Maths despite four attempts
OL,8,Fand is struggling to progress with her
OL,9,Feducation and career.
OL,11,FShe explains: "I can do simple things
OL,12,Flike times tables, money, and reading
OL,13,Fclocks, but when I get to maths exams
OL,14,Fwith things like equations, my brain
OL,15,Fjust gets confused.
OL,17,F"Now I can't apply for certain jobs
OL,18,Fbecause they need GCSE Maths.
