OL,3,CGuernsey students left frustrated over
OL,4,Clow GCSE pass rates for maths
OL,6,F"Applying to uni and applying to get a
OL,7,Fjob, if you are struggling with maths
OL,8,Fand you don't have your maths GCSE,
OL,9,Fwhat do you do?"
OL,11,FAs someone who says it "doesn't really
OL,12,Fclick", Meena needs extra support but
OL,13,Fsays that help often is not there.
OL,15,FShe adds: "It was actually insane the
OL,16,Fturnover of staff leaving and leaving
OL,17,Fand leaving.
OL,19,F"It's quite chaotic and quite
OL,20,Ffrustrating. I'd go to my teachers and
OL,21,Feven they wouldn't know what to do.
