OL,3,CGuernsey students left frustrated over
OL,4,Clow GCSE pass rates for maths
OL,6,F"Especially during lockdown, people
OL,7,Fhave struggled way more and I don't
OL,8,Fthink that there is enough support for
OL,9,Folder people like me who don't know
OL,10,Fwhat to do."
OL,12,FGuernsey maths tutor Sara Parfitt says
OL,13,Fthe number of pupils seeking support
OL,14,Foutside the classroom is rising and
OL,15,Fbelieves the huge turnover in staff is
OL,16,Fthe main reason why.
