OL,3,CGuernsey students left frustrated over
OL,4,Clow GCSE pass rates for maths
OL,6,FShe explains: "At the moment, I'm
OL,7,Falready fully booked until September.
OL,8,FNaturally, I have a waiting list just
OL,9,Fin case people's situation changes but
OL,10,Fit's a big problem.
OL,12,F"One of the biggest things students
OL,13,Fwill say is, 'I had a different
OL,14,Fteacher today, my teacher was at a
OL,15,Fmeeting, my teacher's ill or I've got
OL,16,Fa substitute teacher'.
OL,18,F"As with all subjects, particularly at
OL,19,Fsecondary, if you're not an expert in
OL,20,Fthat subject, it's difficult to teach
OL,21,Fit."
