OL,3,CGuernsey students left frustrated over
OL,4,Clow GCSE pass rates for maths
OL,6,FGuernsey's Director of Education is
OL,7,Fhopeful that results will improve with
OL,8,Fa review to be carried out across all
OL,9,Fthe island's schools to improve maths
OL,10,Fstandards.
OL,12,FThe States of Guernsey says that all
OL,13,Fmaths teacher positions have been
OL,14,Ffilled for next year.
OL,16,FHowever, Paul Montague who represents
OL,17,Fthe National Education Union on the
OL,18,Fisland adds this does not factor in
OL,19,Fstaff retention.
