OL,3,CGuernsey students left frustrated over
OL,4,Clow GCSE pass rates for maths
OL,6,FHe explains: "There's a relocation
OL,7,Fallowance which includes a monthly
OL,8,Fsubsidy for your rental for 36 months
OL,9,Fbut then after two years, they'll
OL,10,Fbegin to look to leave.
OL,12,F"We're talking now in March and
OL,13,Fresignation deadlines aren't until
OL,14,FMay, so I've often heard, 'We've got
OL,15,Fit sorted' but the proof of the
OL,16,Fpudding is what we'll see in
OL,17,FSeptember."
